mangadex.name: Mangadex
mangadex.description:
A website that aggregates scanlated chapters for many manga from many different scanlation groups.
It is the default website that the bot use when fetching manga information.
mangadex.explanation:
Reference type allowed:
#[Manga URL], [Manga ID]
 
Example:
#{0.prefix}sub 39 @member @role
#{0.prefix}sub https://mangadex.org/title/39/One-Piece @member @role
#Subscribes @member and @role to [One Piece]

guyamoe.name: Guya.moe
guyamoe.explanation:
Reference type allowed:
#[Manga URL], [Manga ID], [URL Slug]
 
Example:
#{0.prefix}sub gm1 @member @role
#{0.prefix}sub https://guya.moe/read/manga/Kaguya-Wants-To-Be-Confessed-To/ @member @role
#{0.prefix}sub Kaguya-Wants-To-Be-Confessed-To @member @role
#Subscribes @member and @role to [Kaguya-sama: Love is War]
guyamoe.description:
A website that host high-quality english scanlated chapters for Kaguya-sama related content.
An ID table shown below represents the manga hosted on the website
```
[gm1] : Kaguya-sama: Love is War
[gm2] : Kaguya Wants To Be Confessed To Official Doujin
[gm3] : We Want To Talk About Kaguya
```
